Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.60,0:21:37.75,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,That's the kind of mistake my mom would make!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:39.91,Main01,OTAE,0,0,0,,Yes, yes. I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.92,0:21:40.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(お妙)はいはい わかりましたよ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:45.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.22,0:21:47.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…すまねえな｡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.76,0:21:47.03,Main01,GINTOKI,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.88,0:21:50.68,Main01,MAN A,0,0,0,,Watch it, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:51.26,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,(男)気をつけろ！ この野郎!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.26,0:22:00.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,♪♪～
